neyn, neyn, eyn minut. ikh, dos iz a zakh vos iz farknipt mit andere zakhn.

00:11:41.404 --> 00:11:43.541
es iz farknipt eyn z-...

00:11:42.535 --> 00:11:43.845
nemt tsayt!

00:11:43.750 --> 00:11:44.503
⟨nu⟩...

00:11:45.927 --> 00:11:54.140
kh'bin, ⟨, dos⟩, gevezn v⟨UNK⟩... yo, bin ikh gekumen un kh'hob geforn avek keyn,

00:11:54.162 --> 00:11:56.991
genumen keyn, Zakopane.

00:11:57.064 --> 00:11:58.993
un fun Zakopane,

00:11:58.993 --> 00:12:04.601
ze'mir gegat dem shmukler, un der shmukler hot undz aribergefirt keyn Slovakay.

00:12:05.198 --> 00:12:08.610
keyn Slovakay. dos iz nokh gevezn tsurik,

00:12:08.610 --> 00:12:12.660
az ikh bin gevezn in, in,

00:12:12.707 --> 00:12:15.181
bay Zakopane. Zakopane iz dokh Poyln.

00:12:16.150 --> 00:12:18.759
⟨un nokh dem ze'mir⟩ gekumen...

00:12:19.491 --> 00:12:21.240
UNK bin ikh gekumen

00:12:22.157 --> 00:12:26.480
keyn UNK ⟨Zakopane,⟩ bin ikh gekumen keyn, ⟨⟩...

00:12:26.480 --> 00:12:30.099
un THEN bin ikh ge- geforn...

00:12:30.310 --> 00:12:33.103
yo, keyn, tsu der grenets,

00:12:33.126 --> 00:12:36.090
un fun der grenets bin ikh geforn

00:12:36.417 --> 00:12:40.790
keyn Sh- Sh- nisht keyn Sh⟨UNK⟩...

00:12:41.080 --> 00:12:45.118
sh- shva- m'hot tseshvartst,

00:12:46.592 --> 00:12:51.100
gekumen... yo, s'hot gedoyert, s'iz geku- kh'bin gekum- bin geforn keyn,

00:12:51.100 --> 00:12:52.458
fun Kasho,

00:12:52.549 --> 00:12:56.646
fun Ka- far Kasho bin ikh geforn fun Zakopane

00:12:56.646 --> 00:12:59.820
un kh'bin gekumen keyn Slovakay.

00:12:59.907 --> 00:13:03.280
in Slovakay bin ikh geven epes a tsvey tog

00:13:03.467 --> 00:13:06.515
un kh'bin geforn keyn Kasho.

00:13:06.876 --> 00:13:13.176
in Kasho bin ikh geven, g- bin ikh gevezn, hobn mikh, hobn mentshn,

00:13:13.176 --> 00:13:15.816
hot men gefirt, ungarishe UNK

00:13:15.816 --> 00:13:19.020
di ungarn hobn gefirt... Ungarn iz geven fray nokh,

00:13:19.020 --> 00:13:24.850
nor m'hot gekent forn UNK. bin ikh gegangen, kh'hob mikh aroyfgez- kh'- bin ikh ge- ikh hob dokh gegat PAPERS.

00:13:24.850 --> 00:13:27.739
ikh bin dokh a ungarisher birger f⟨UNK⟩.

00:13:27.739 --> 00:13:30.900
UNK iz,

00:13:31.024 --> 00:13:32.953
UNK ⟨ge⟩kumen in Ungarn,

00:13:32.953 --> 00:13:35.490
hob ikh,... yo! dos meydl.

00:13:35.817 --> 00:13:41.840
iz ge- hot men, kh'bin arayngegangen in a shil arayn. hot men in shil gezogt, "do bistu a DANGER."

00:13:41.840 --> 00:13:46.730
far vos? vayl di, ⟨z- me,⟩ zey kumen, zey hobn dokh gevust az me shmuklt

00:13:46.785 --> 00:13:50.593
dort, hot men moyre gegat, vayl s'iz dokh geven nisht bloyz shmuklers dort.

00:13:50.633 --> 00:13:51.996
hobn zey gevust.

00:13:51.996 --> 00:13:59.401
hobn zey nisht, hobn zey nisht gevolt haltn undz in besmedresh, nor bahaltn ergets in a, in a keler,

00:13:59.492 --> 00:14:02.970
biz m'hot, m'hot ⟨z-⟩ erleydikt,

00:14:02.970 --> 00:14:04.886
me zol forn keyn Ungarn.

00:14:05.550 --> 00:14:08.446
me zol forn keyn Ungarn. Kasho iz oykhet Ungarn,

00:14:08.537 --> 00:14:12.041
nor vos den? dos iz bay der grenets mit Slovakay.

00:14:12.132 --> 00:14:16.130
ze- nu, ze'mir aroyfgezetst zikh oyf der TRAIN. ze'mir geven fir yinglekh.

00:14:16.266 --> 00:14:20.208
UNK oyfgezetst oyf der TRAIN un, nu, m'iz geforn mit der TRAIN.

00:14:20.265 --> 00:14:22.422
un lebn Mishkolts,

00:14:22.422 --> 00:14:24.107
lebn Mishkolts efsher,

00:14:24.872 --> 00:14:27.211
me halt, kumt aroyf di,

00:14:27.218 --> 00:14:30.334
di mit di kapelitshn, di CSENDŐRes heysn zey.

00:14:30.711 --> 00:14:32.270
un kumen aroyf,

00:14:32.652 --> 00:14:34.502
un me halt undz:

00:14:35.537 --> 00:14:36.611
"PAPERS."

00:14:37.123 --> 00:14:44.862
vayl s'iz ge- vayl, dos meydl iz dokh shuldik geven, vos m⟨it-⟩ zi iz mitgeforn mit undz, ⟨vos, mit-⟩ mitgeshikt a meydl f- a ungarish meydl

00:14:44.920 --> 00:14:50.030
hot men mitgeshikt. iz zi zikh gegangen, zi hot zikh gezetst in yener zayt CAR,

00:14:50.134 --> 00:14:53.961
un mi- un- un mir ho- undz... ze'mir geven fir yinglekh...

00:14:53.961 --> 00:14:55.781
hot ⟨er⟩ gelozt zitsn tsuzamen.

00:14:55.821 --> 00:14:59.927
beheyme! ⟨z⟩ets yedemen SEPARATE, vel'mir dokh nisht oyffaln!

00:14:59.927 --> 00:15:03.948
do hobn zey gegebn a kum op un m'hot gezen, di fir khevre zits'mir tsuzamen:

00:15:03.972 --> 00:15:08.086
o-o! dos iz epes, epe- epes iz do nisht, epes kosher.

00:15:08.086 --> 00:15:10.834
zitsn mir fir, un zits'mir bar a tishele.

00:15:11.228 --> 00:15:14.951
un m'hot undz ale genumen in JAIL arayn,

00:15:15.430 --> 00:15:17.364
in ⟨der, dort⟩ UNK.

00:15:17.370 --> 00:15:24.066
UNK JAIL arayn, un m'hot undz gefirt in a TOLONC-hoyz. dort in dem TOLONC-hoyz iz a,

00:15:24.066 --> 00:15:25.245
vos me ken

00:15:25.800 --> 00:15:29.970
khapn oreme-layt vos zey zitsn, zey raysn, zey ganvenen

00:15:30.010 --> 00:15:32.670
UNK nemt men zey arayn in dem TOLONC-HOUSE.

00:15:32.676 --> 00:15:40.635
un ⟨m- z-⟩ mir zenen gezitsn dort anderhalbn tog, biz m'iz gevoyer gevorn fun di yidn az n⟨akh⟩ zitsn dray, fir yidn,

00:15:40.708 --> 00:15:44.440
⟨iz men⟩ gegangen un m'hot zey, m'hot undz aroysgenumen.

00:15:43.740 --> 00:15:48.431
 dos iz geven di d- vel- ver iz geven di politsey? di ungarishe?

00:15:47.037 --> 00:15:51.283
di politsey? ungarishe, ungarishe, di vos, mit di HATS mit di federn.

00:15:51.627 --> 00:15:54.388
UNK geven, geheysn di CSENDŐRes.

00:15:54.394 --> 00:16:00.888
haklal, m'hot undz gehaltn anderhalbn tog in JAIL, dort in ⟨g-,⟩ in ⟨mi-⟩ dem ho- in dem hoyz,

00:16:00.888 --> 00:16:03.180
vos shnorers,

00:16:03.180 --> 00:16:06.051
UNK ganvenen a broyt ⟨g-⟩ zetst men dort arayn,

00:16:06.051 --> 00:16:08.174
shoyn a- farshidene azoyne.

00:16:08.400 --> 00:16:14.430
m'hot undz aroysgelozt in anderhalbn tog, un m'hot undz genumen, un m'hot undz avekgefirt

00:16:14.526 --> 00:16:16.446
⟨D⟩ifer un Ungarn.

00:16:16.446 --> 00:16:19.020
nor vos den? me ken nisht, me, di,

00:16:19.020 --> 00:16:22.418
ikh bin fray arumtsugeyn in, in lager,

00:16:22.542 --> 00:16:25.002
un oysern lager ken ikh nisht geyn,

00:16:25.002 --> 00:16:27.630
nor ⟨t⟩saydn a POLICEMAN geyt mit ⟨dir⟩.

00:16:28.060 --> 00:16:29.167
⟨un tomer iz ge-...⟩

00:16:28.279 --> 00:16:30.315
 avoser lager iz dos geven?

00:16:30.068 --> 00:16:33.268
dos iz geven aza, a, a internirungs-lager.

00:16:33.460 --> 00:16:35.175
in velekher shtot?

00:16:34.827 --> 00:16:40.628
dos iz geven take in, in mitn veg dort, vu, ikh veys, ⟨K-⟩ CSÖRGŐ heyst es.

00:16:40.628 --> 00:16:42.768
ikh veys vu dos iz? CSÖRGŐ.

00:16:42.825 --> 00:16:45.468
in CSÖ- un dort bin ikh gezitsn

00:16:45.829 --> 00:16:48.130
a ⟨p-⟩ a sheyne por monat.

00:16:48.310 --> 00:16:50.751
veys nisht, tsi akht monat tsi, ⟨⟩...

00:16:50.858 --> 00:16:52.978
a sheyne por monat.

00:16:53.119 --> 00:16:56.680
un m'hot mikh aroy- m- biz,

00:16:56.680 --> 00:16:58.664
biz m'hot gelozt aroysgeyn.

00:16:59.987 --> 00:17:02.546
shoyn. un m'iz aroysgegangen.

00:17:02.063 --> 00:17:06.360
velekhn, ven zent ir aroysgegan? velekhn yor, velekhn monat?

00:17:06.348 --> 00:17:10.680
aroysgegangen⟨, iz,⟩ zikher, ⟨⟩...

00:17:11.344 --> 00:17:13.200
in ⟨d- d-⟩ in...

00:17:13.318 --> 00:17:17.078
kh'bin nokh nisht geven fray in gantsn, vayl ikh bin, ⟨ikh hob⟩ nokh gemuzt ⟨zayn⟩ UNK.

00:17:17.078 --> 00:17:23.685
nor vos den? in dray un fertsik hob ikh gezogt. ⟨iz ikh, iz, g-⟩ ze'mir geven, m'hot undz dort gezitsn, ze'mir gezitsn dort a,

00:17:23.685 --> 00:17:25.479
a por sheyne monat,

00:17:25.502 --> 00:17:31.900
un, ah, ⟨ze'mir⟩, m'hot undz aroy- m'hot undz avekgeshikt...

00:17:34.311 --> 00:17:36.330
ay, ay, ay...

00:17:40.450 --> 00:17:41.860
UNK

00:17:42.748 --> 00:17:44.530
 ver hot aykh avekgeshikt?

00:17:44.436 --> 00:17:47.318
di ungarishe shoyn, di ungarishe POLICE.

00:17:47.318 --> 00:17:50.808
iz, koydem iz, ikh bin gevezn,

00:17:51.152 --> 00:17:56.370
hob ikh gegangen fun Ungarn UNK...

00:17:59.840 --> 00:18:07.690
fun Ungarn... fun Ungarn hot men dokh z- undz vayter arayngezetst in der khad-gadye, un, un...

00:18:11.790 --> 00:18:14.855
ven m'hot aykh aroysgelozt fun tfise dortn,

00:18:14.592 --> 00:18:15.531
yo?

00:18:14.912 --> 00:18:18.078
vu zent ir gegan vayter, nokh der tfise in Ungarn?

00:18:18.650 --> 00:18:21.285
 n- nokh in Ungarn gegangen.

00:18:20.937 --> 00:18:23.530
vu hot ir gevoynt shpeter, nokh der tfise?

00:18:23.603 --> 00:18:25.774
nokh der tfise in Ungarn,

00:18:25.797 --> 00:18:28.060
bin ikh dokh gevoynt...

00:18:28.935 --> 00:18:31.949
UNK gemuzt zayn shoyn fir un fertsiker yor.

00:18:31.430 --> 00:18:33.890
vos hot pasirt in fir un fertsikstn yor?

00:18:32.901 --> 00:18:33.890
ha?

00:18:34.538 --> 00:18:37.164
vos hot pasirt in fir un fertsikstn yor?

00:18:42.891 --> 00:18:43.729
ir...

00:18:52.172 --> 00:18:55.676
ir gedenkt di doytshn, ⟨v-⟩ araynkumen in Ungarn?

00:18:56.610 --> 00:19:00.333
ikh bi- di doytshn zenen gekumen tsu Ungarn f- BEFORE ME.

00:19:00.660 --> 00:19:03.410
ikh bin gekumen, zenen di doytshn shoyn geven dort,

00:19:03.410 --> 00:19:10.860
ober di doytshn hobn zikh nisht gekent mishn gornisht, vayl s'iz, di ungarishe BEHÖRDE hot dokh gegat, zey hobn dokh nisht gekent zikh mishn.

00:19:11.933 --> 00:19:14.081
 nor vi azoy iz dos ge-... o!

00:19:14.081 --> 00:19:15.825
fir un fertsik...

00:19:21.163 --> 00:19:22.979
fir un fertsik...

00:19:24.083 --> 00:19:28.430
tsi dray un UNK tsi f- do fe- do felt epes.

00:19:28.555 --> 00:19:33.720
⟨,⟩ dray un fertsik, ⟨dos⟩ heyst in fir un fertsik bin ikh gevezn...

00:19:44.788 --> 00:19:47.330
ven m'hot aykh aroysgelozt fun tfise,

00:19:47.751 --> 00:19:48.751
yo.

00:19:48.147 --> 00:19:51.651
vu zent ir gegangen vayter? m'hot aykh geshikt ergets

00:19:51.825 --> 00:19:53.020
fun Ungarn...

00:19:51.977 --> 00:19:53.422
fun der tfise?

00:19:53.293 --> 00:19:56.172
fun der tfise hot men mikh geshikt keyn CSÖRGŐ.

00:19:56.517 --> 00:20:01.708
d- d- kh'bin geven anderhalbn tog, un fun di anderhalbn tog hot men undz geshikt keyn CSÖRGŐ.

00:19:59.942 --> 00:20:04.121
NO, NO, NO, NO. nokh dem vos ir ⟨zen⟩t gezesn a por khadoshim in tfise.

00:20:05.697 --> 00:20:06.920
ir gedenkt?

00:20:06.920 --> 00:20:10.398
a por khadoshim zent ir gezesn, "a sheyne por khadoshim" zogt ir.

00:20:10.742 --> 00:20:12.739
yo, UNK, zikher.

00:20:12.739 --> 00:20:15.780
vi az- ober vi azoy bin ikh dort ⟨gegangen⟩?

00:20:17.290 --> 00:20:20.254
ir zent a mol geven in a kontsentratsye-lager?

00:20:21.306 --> 00:20:23.983
zikher! vos heyst? kh'bin dokh geven in Oyshvits.

00:20:23.685 --> 00:20:26.024
vi azoy zent ir gekumen keyn AUSCHWITZ?

00:20:25.710 --> 00:20:28.322
o, keyn Oyshvits veys ikh vi UNK gekumen,

00:20:28.225 --> 00:20:29.417
vi azoy?

00:20:28.322 --> 00:20:30.311
nor biz tsu Oyshvits,

00:20:30.857 --> 00:20:33.990
biz Oyshvits iz dokh epes mer geve- felt dokh mir.

00:20:35.802 --> 00:20:39.593
⟨in, bin in⟩ Oyshvits, bin ikh gevezn in,

00:20:40.813 --> 00:20:41.954
..

00:20:44.914 --> 00:20:45.718
v⟨i⟩...

00:20:47.270 --> 00:20:51.880
f- f- ikh vil far Oyshvits nokh...

00:20:52.795 --> 00:20:58.762
vi azoy zent ir gekumen keyn AUSCHWITZ? vi azoy hot es oysgezen? vi azoy hot men aykh geshikt keyn AUSCHWITZ?

00:20:59.697 --> 00:21:02.694
Oyshvits iz gevezn mit a...

00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:09.540
dos iz...

00:21:10.830 --> 00:21:14.530
dray... lomir zen, tsvey un fertsik UNK

00:21:14.530 --> 00:21:16.770
gegangen keyn Ungarn f⟨UNK⟩.

00:21:16.770 --> 00:21:22.570
nokh dem bin ikh ⟨g- shoyn⟩ dray ⟨un fertsik⟩ bin ikh geven in UNK⟨er, dos⟩...

00:21:29.900 --> 00:21:33.728
 s'zet oys, fun dray un fertsik

00:21:34.003 --> 00:21:39.280
ze'mir gefo- ze'mir arayn i- i- in Oyshvits.

00:21:39.218 --> 00:21:42.064
vi azoy iz dos, ver hot aykh geshikt ahin?

00:21:41.783 --> 00:21:43.948
d- ve- dort keyn Oyshvits?

00:21:43.948 --> 00:21:47.960
s'iz geven genug shikers UNK...

00:21:46.828 --> 00:21:49.269
in dray un fertsik iz dos geven?

00:21:49.461 --> 00:21:51.952
a minut... yo, s'zet azoy oys.

00:21:50.440 --> 00:21:53.404
ir zent zikher az s'iz geven in dray un fertsik?

00:21:52.532 --> 00:21:53.946
UNK dray un fertsik.

00:21:53.946 --> 00:22:01.800
un THEN hot men undz, in dray un fertsik ho'mir un- hot men undz arayngeshikt, m'hot undz arayngebrengt

00:22:01.864 --> 00:22:06.730
in f- dray un ⟨f- d-⟩ fertsik tsi in fir un f- tsi fir un fertsik.

00:22:06.730 --> 00:22:08.434
UNK fir un fertsik

00:22:08.434 --> 00:22:12.830
ho'mir un- hot men undz sh- bafrayt...

00:22:13.035 --> 00:22:17.670
NO, nisht bafrayt. s'iz geven in Ungarn, un,

00:22:18.013 --> 00:22:22.670
un THEN hot men undz, in Ungarn hot men undz ar-

00:22:22.820 --> 00:22:29.650
⟨g- in⟩ Ungarn hot men undz gehaltn biz,

00:22:30.822 --> 00:22:32.740
biz finef un fertsik.

00:22:32.931 --> 00:22:38.949
fir, in dray un fertsik, ende, iz, UNK ho- hot men undz genumen keyn AUSCHWITZ,

00:22:38.854 --> 00:22:41.432
vi azoy? ir gedenkt,

00:22:38.955 --> 00:22:41.970
un mir ze'mir geven akht, nayn monat.

00:22:41.432 --> 00:22:44.281
ir gedenkt ven m'hot aykh genemen keyn AUSCHWITZ?

00:22:44.254 --> 00:22:46.104
dos gedenk ikh yo.

00:22:45.317 --> 00:22:46.931
dertseylt mir derfun.

00:22:46.380 --> 00:22:54.320
di akht, di, v- vayl m'hot undz ge- ven m'hot undz gebrengt,...

00:22:58.430 --> 00:23:00.616
⟨fun Bokhnye keyn⟩ UNK

00:23:00.673 --> 00:23:06.360
fun d- dort hot men undz vayter geshikt keyn Oyshvits.

00:23:08.554 --> 00:23:14.808
ven mir zenen geven in dray un fertsik, hot men undz aray- hot men undz arayngezetst in,

00:23:15.102 --> 00:23:17.800
in a, a lager,

00:23:17.800 --> 00:23:19.283
vos s'iz nisht gevezn,

00:23:19.283 --> 00:23:24.506
vos s'iz nisht gevezn, m'hot nisht ge- geshlogn, m'hot nisht geharget, m'hot nisht gornisht getun.

00:23:24.506 --> 00:23:29.253
nor vos den? m'hot undz avekgezetst, un dort ze'mir gezitsn azoy lang

00:23:29.277 --> 00:23:32.270
biz m'hot undz aribergefirt

00:23:32.280 --> 00:23:37.710
keyn, keyn, keyn Oyshvits damols.

00:23:37.748 --> 00:23:40.560
mit Oyshvits... un m'iz friert nisht gevezn.

00:23:42.422 --> 00:23:45.757
vi azoy, ir gedenkt ven ir zent ongekumen keyn AUSCHWITZ?

00:23:45.865 --> 00:23:52.480
dos ⟨ged-⟩ ongekumen ⟨da- d- es⟩ gefelt mir vi azoy UNK...

00:23:51.265 --> 00:23:54.229
mit avoser tsug zent ir geforn keyn AUSCHWITZ?

00:23:54.100 --> 00:24:03.156
mit a ba- UNK a, dos, a tsug mit, ⟨TRAI- p-⟩ pasazhirn-tsug. UNK undz hot men arayngezetst in di vagonen, nisht in, me,

00:23:57.053 --> 00:23:58.819
a pasazhirn-tsug?

00:24:03.263 --> 00:24:08.437
d- di vagonen vos me firt, di, dos, di khazeyrim.

00:24:09.120 --> 00:24:13.905
⟨v-⟩ hot men undz arayngezetst, zet oys, azoy...

00:24:16.645 --> 00:24:25.194
ven di NYILASes... ir vey-, ir v- di NYILASes hobn banumen dort di, di, di memshole,

00:24:25.791 --> 00:24:28.383
un m'hot HORTHY avekgezetst.

00:24:28.744 --> 00:24:34.037
iz men gekum-, nu, iz dokh gevezn, ze'mir dokh vayter geven in TROUBLE,

00:24:34.397 --> 00:24:37.560
vayl kh'hob dokh shoyn gemuzt, vayter zayn in lager,

00:24:37.560 --> 00:24:40.753
vayl zey hobn dokh ibergenumen, di NYILASes,

00:24:40.810 --> 00:24:43.149
un zey zenen dokh geven, ⟨, di⟩ groyse reshoim,

00:24:43.270 --> 00:24:46.457
⟨zenen⟩ dokh geven, dos. a yid?! ⟨iz er⟩ geven UNK.

00:24:46.480 --> 00:24:48.830
un in fir un fertsik

00:24:48.960 --> 00:24:50.540
hot men undz...

